  <entry>
    <title>利用torch.optim.SGD类实例最小化函数f(x)</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2019/07/18/%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8torch.optim.SGD%E7%B1%BB%E5%AE%9E%E4%BE%8B%E6%9C%80%E5%B0%8F%E5%8C%96%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0f(x)/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2019/07/18/利用torch.optim.SGD类实例最小化函数f(x)/</id>
    <published>2019-07-18T05:40:55.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-07-18T05:59:25.743Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="如题"><a href="#如题" class="headerlink" title="如题"></a>如题</h3><a id="more"></a><h5 id="–来自于肖志清的《神经网络与pytorch实战》"><a href="#–来自于肖志清的《神经网络与pytorch实战》" class="headerlink" title="–来自于肖志清的《神经网络与pytorch实战》"></a>–来自于肖志清的《神经网络与pytorch实战》</h5><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> math <span class="keyword">import</span> pi</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> torch</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">x = torch.tensor([pi/<span class="number">3</span>, pi/<span class="number">6</span>], requires_grad=<span class="literal">True</span>) <span class="comment"># 输入的数</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> torch.optim <span class="keyword">as</span> optim</span><br><span class="line">optimzer = optim.SGD([x,], lr=<span class="number">0.1</span>, momentum=<span class="number">0</span>)<span class="comment"># 第一个参数是需要更新的列表。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> step <span class="keyword">in</span> range(<span class="number">11</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># step为0时，没有优化，从1开始优化。</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> step:</span><br><span class="line">        optimzer.zero_grad() <span class="comment"># 需要清空优化器在上次迭代中存储的数据。避免积累。</span></span><br><span class="line">        f.backward()<span class="comment"># 调用这个方法，说明进行求导。</span></span><br><span class="line">        optimzer.step()<span class="comment"># 用这个方法更新自变量的值</span></span><br><span class="line">    f = -((x.cos() ** <span class="number">2</span>).sum()) ** <span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line">    print(<span class="string">'step &#123;&#125; : x = &#123;&#125;, f(x) = &#123;&#125;'</span>.format(step, x.tolist(), f))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h6 id="输出："><a href="#输出：" class="headerlink" title="输出："></a>输出：</h6><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">step <span class="number">0</span> : x = [<span class="number">1.0471975803375244</span>, <span class="number">0.5235987901687622</span>], f(x) = <span class="number">-1.0</span></span><br><span class="line">step <span class="number">1</span> : x = [<span class="number">0.8739925026893616</span>, <span class="number">0.35039371252059937</span>], f(x) = <span class="number">-1.674528956413269</span></span><br><span class="line">step <span class="number">2</span> : x = [<span class="number">0.6192374229431152</span>, <span class="number">0.1835097223520279</span>], f(x) = <span class="number">-2.6563119888305664</span></span><br><span class="line">step <span class="number">3</span> : x = [<span class="number">0.3111077845096588</span>, <span class="number">0.06654246151447296</span>], f(x) = <span class="number">-3.617122173309326</span></span><br><span class="line">step <span class="number">4</span> : x = [<span class="number">0.08941137790679932</span>, <span class="number">0.016069628298282623</span>], f(x) = <span class="number">-3.9671425819396973</span></span><br><span class="line">step <span class="number">5</span> : x = [<span class="number">0.01855570822954178</span>, <span class="number">0.0032690390944480896</span>], f(x) = <span class="number">-3.99858021736145</span></span><br><span class="line">step <span class="number">6</span> : x = [<span class="number">0.0037171822041273117</span>, <span class="number">0.0006542906630784273</span>], f(x) = <span class="number">-3.999943256378174</span></span><br><span class="line">step <span class="number">7</span> : x = [<span class="number">0.0007434850558638573</span>, <span class="number">0.00013086199760437012</span>], f(x) = <span class="number">-3.999997615814209</span></span><br><span class="line">step <span class="number">8</span> : x = [<span class="number">0.00014869740698486567</span>, <span class="number">2.617243444547057e-05</span>], f(x) = <span class="number">-4.0</span></span><br><span class="line">step <span class="number">9</span> : x = [<span class="number">2.973947994178161e-05</span>, <span class="number">5.234485797700472e-06</span>], f(x) = <span class="number">-4.0</span></span><br><span class="line">step <span class="number">10</span> : x = [<span class="number">5.947895260760561e-06</span>, <span class="number">1.0468970685906243e-06</span>], f(x) = <span class="number">-4.0</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
